{"tid":2321334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國挑釁意味濃？王晨出席中國美國商會年度晚宴","createTime":"2020-12-11T12:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T14:14:39.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4118f837bdd110c0c34e78d5fcf4499c9fbbc7","tid":2321334,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"美國政府週一以中國破壞香港民主程序為由，制裁14中國全國人大常委會副委員長，而美國商會10日晚間在中國舉行年度晚宴，中國派出的出席代表，就是制裁名單上的中國人大副委員長王晨，引發外界聯想。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報導，美國週一宣布，對14位中國人大常委會副委員長實施制裁，依據相關措施，受制裁者及其直系親屬未來將禁止入境美國，其在美或由美國他人持有、控制資產，均將遭凍結。<br />\n<br />\n昨日在中國的美國商會舉行年度晚宴，而中方派出官方代表王晨，王晨即是被美方制裁的名單之一，更是中國人大常委會副委員長中，黨內職務最高的一人。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，往年中方大多派遣與商業、經濟領域相關的行政高官與會；去年適逢中國美國商會成立100週年，中方指派國務院副總理胡春華出席。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">對此，在中國的美國商會主席吉利根（Greg Gilligan）在電子郵件聲明中表示：「本週的其他事態發展涉及政治考慮，我們不參與其中。」這是指對2國官員互相實行的制裁措施。他稱，「我們是一個獨立的組織，旨在代表我們的會員成為美國和中國之間的商業橋樑」。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，報導提到，與會的中國與全球化智庫 （Center for China and Globalization）主席Henry Wang說，王晨在談話中完全沒有提及制裁一事，他的談話內容「完全友好」，他則認為，中國派此委員表明中國對待這一事件的高度重視。<br />\n<br />\n美國大使館發言人拒絕對王晨的出席發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3378645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3378645&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=61e8b803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3378645&h=aa00a836\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3378645</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-11/china-sends-sanctioned-official-to-amcham-dinner-in-beijing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-12-11%2Fchina-sends-sanctioned-official-to-amcham-dinner-in-beijing&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=4f78bd30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-11/china-sends-sanctioned-official-to-amcham-dinner-in-beijing</a>"},{"pid":"928fef4c10ad036ba20ce283fc57dd69a58904e6","tid":2321334,"uid":2545,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"反制措施之一黎<br />\n我地呢啲蟻民唔會明"},{"pid":"a2ba351c903f22c6804d268a1d2c9733d2ca62a8","tid":2321334,"uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"一班賣國賊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8e96bf58ae3d3b26e77f144640f3467e4eafc5","tid":2321334,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"中共：制裁？未驚過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e89857b6b75d0b0802a0725f9a440e8bdded14","tid":2321334,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"傾下點走資？"},{"pid":"4cfedd38238aabbedc82774e3b1520cc6985b74c","tid":2321334,"uid":26708,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"中共同華爾街叛徒未驚過喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美元大佬要加把勁叫佢堆細大大力打擊中共"},{"pid":"96cd63fd7fbe8ab6bbf22ee0f8b4a4f751dcd145","tid":2321334,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"奶共商會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a55d447e1db1ad1c5791aab303a87f09cb8d6c","tid":2321334,"uid":280593,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:43:10.000Z","msg":"去唔到美國,去下美國商會晚宴都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2104b434f6522fbb42dcbd47a425283e2aae6e19","tid":2321334,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"在中國的美國商會主席吉利根"},{"pid":"be2da26114c8639e33a4f6be55a465d522423698","tid":2321334,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score"